{"tid":2233119,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"62%港人反對警改傳媒定義","createTime":"2020-10-07T01:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T01:44:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6ab633d432a299e47443fd3f92d384429adba9","tid":2233119,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:39:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/3KUCERHMUNHGLOIBBBMJHF35YI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2F3KUCERHMUNHGLOIBBBMJHF35YI%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmSYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=cea5c61a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2F3KUCERHMUNHGLOIBBBMJHF35YI%2F&h=104a6056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/3KUCERHMUNHGLOIBBBMJHF35YI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n62%港人反對警改傳媒定義<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cxQ4u2rfzmOckPEs4mLPqSCox8k=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YN7ESY2YWZA2JJMTBE3BM6QYOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcxQ4u2rfzmOckPEs4mLPqSCox8k%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYN7ESY2YWZA2JJMTBE3BM6QYOE.jpg&h=9647cfbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方變本加厲打壓傳媒惹大眾不滿。<br />\n<br />\n【香港民研】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方早前修訂《警察通例》中「傳媒代表」定義，將網媒和學生記者排除在外。香港民意研究所就此進行民調，發現62%受訪者反對警方做法，36%受訪者表示支持。浸大傳理學院新聞系前助理教授杜耀明認為，數據反映市民對政策的不滿，若不能撥亂反正，市民不滿程度有可能再提高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n31%建制支持者拒撐<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所公佈有關警方近日修訂「傳媒代表」定義進行民調，調查以電郵訪問11,432名12歲以上的受訪者，發現62%受訪者反對警方做法，其中高達58%人表明「好反對」，36%受訪者表示支持。若將受訪者以政治立場劃分，多達97%民主派支持者反對警方做法，受訪的建制派支持者中，則有65%人表示支持，也有31%人表示反對警方做法。<br />\n<br />\n杜耀明認為調查結果反映市民不滿警方壟斷記者定義，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於有31%受訪的建制派支持者也反對警方做法，杜耀明指，建制陣營也有網媒為受眾提供即時資訊，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"bccbaee63f4b674263d4d301ac456e9daf5b88dc","tid":2233119,"uid":108462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"話知你62%定100%反對 政府都唔會理你<br />\n這就是獨裁政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}